item.title: CVE-2020-5377|2024-08-04T08:30:23.924Z -- dell -- dell%20open%20manage%20server%20administrator
item.description: Dell EMC OpenManage Server Administrator (OMSA) versions 9.4 and prior contain multiple path traversal vulnerabilities. An unauthenticated remote attacker could potentially exploit these vulnerabilities by sending a crafted Web API request containing directory traversal character sequences to gain file system access on the compromised management station.
